+	/*
+	 * GPIO107 = vendor GPIO_OTG_DRVVBUS_PIN (aeon6797_6m_n.dws:1561),
+	 * hardware enable gate for the BQ25896 OTG boost. LK hands over
+	 * with it LOW and the boost then fails SILENTLY (no fault bits) —
+	 * live-proven 2026-07-14 (B-19 Stage C Phase 0, run v5): with the
+	 * OTG register bit already set, VBUS only appeared once devmem
